abstractText: In this data file, the synthetic procedures for the preparation of a series of anticancer tetrazolato-bridged dinuclear platinum(II) complexes ([{cis-Pt(NH3)2}2(μ-OH)(μ-5-R-tetrazolato-N2,N3)]n+ (n = 1 or 2, tetrazolato-bridged complexes)) and of the bridging ligands of 5-substituted 1H-tetrazoles (5-R-1H-tetrazoles) are described. These compounds were characterized by 1H-, 13C-, 19F- and 195Pt-NMR spectroscopy and mass spectrometry.
